title: DARK'S Top 10 WORST Character Fates Ranked!
author: Think Story
comment: #1 worst fate = me because I have no more Dark episodes 😭 Which character do you think had it the worst?
When Ulrich is waiting for Katarina..breaks my heart.
Where’s Mikkel? Of all the characters on the list, Mikkel would have been the only one who didn’t deserve his fate. He didn’t even hurt anyone.
Where is the secretary of Claudia, she had to reschedule every meeting of Claudia and at last she was killed
Katherina’s death was heartbreaking. A tired mother just trying to get her son back only to be killed by her own mother.
description:
Netflix's DARK spans 3 seasons of time travelling, but which character had it the worst? In this video I rank the top 10 characters who had it the worst.
